### B2 Â· Hover Alternate Image
**File:** [storefront/src/components/ProductGrid.tsx](file:///e:/Kvastram%20projects/kvastram-platform/storefront/src/components/ProductGrid.tsx)  
**Why:** Fashion e-commerce mein hover image swap standard UX hai.

**Changes:**
- `product.images[1]` check karo (second image)
- CSS `opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100` transition use karo
- Dono images ek saath render karo, second ko initially hide karo

```tsx
{product.images?.[1] && (
  <OptimizedImage
    src={product.images[1].url}
    alt={`${product.title} alternate view`}
    fill
    className="object-cover opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 absolute inset-0"
  />
)}
```

> [!NOTE]
> `product.images` type mein pehle se `ProductImage[]` hai â€” TypeScript safe hai.

